profile:
Kelly Heaps has been the Owner of Heaps of Decor since 2004 which specializes in home decor and interior design.  In 2008 the company expanded into Home Staging with a division called home stating top sales.  

I offer my clients a leading edge in preparing homes for sale and with my creative edge, my talent in staging and interior design comes alive with creations that evoke true emotion and exciting ambiance.

I enjoy the process of each project, getting to know my clients and listening to their wants and needs.  It's exciting to transform my clients homes into something better than they imagined and in the process alleviating some of their stress and easing the transition
